# hard: deep-diagnosis + adjacent/interaction fixture (dual-use with the
# live "hard" playground PR). Repeated 3x by default since the whole point
# is measuring right-line-wrong-mechanism and adjacent-scope recall, which
# are noisy signals at k=1. No must-catch: recall_deep/recall_adjacent are
# the numbers this fixture exists to produce, not a pass/fail gate.
RUNS_DEFAULT=3
